{"tid":1026690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只是「前僱員」… 香港賽馬會正式聲明戳破韓國瑜賽馬「夢」","createTime":"2019-02-18T09:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T11:17:20.000Z","uid":35221,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c69d49612e9dc6ca747d7dae80fdd42232e0ddcf","tid":1026690,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"只是「前僱員」&hellip; 香港馬會正式聲明戳破韓國瑜賽馬「夢」<br />\n新頭殼newtalk | 吳賜山 綜合報導<br />\n發布 2019.02.18 | 17:18<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/209/5c6a76e58d81e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F209%2F5c6a76e58d81e.jpg&h=e337ebc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港馬會正式發表聲明，表示「從沒有跟高雄市政府就發展賽馬的計劃進行討論」。 圖：香港賽馬會郵件截圖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/203/5c51847f1d0ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F203%2F5c51847f1d0ab.jpg&h=76159586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港馬會前董事林雋軒拜訪韓國瑜，討論高市賽馬產業議題。 圖：高雄市政府/提供<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜就職前拋出高雄發展賽馬產業的構想，還煞有其事地與前香港馬會成員董事林雋軒會面，建構出帶動周邊8大產業，增加9.6萬就業人口，並可產生2700億到3000億元左右的營收的美夢。對此，香港賽馬會特別發表聲明，強調馬會從沒有跟高雄市政府就發展賽馬的計劃進行討論。<br />\n<br />\n香港賽馬會指韓國瑜接受媒體訪問題時提到，「已協助他們『打造了一個需求表』，包括土地、空間及設施等需求」部份不實。馬會指「從沒有跟高雄市政府就他們發展賽馬的計劃進行討論」、「沒有參與任何相關的工作，包括韓國瑜市長所提及的土地、空間及設施等需求評估」；直接挑明「任何馬會前僱員就高雄賽馬發展的參與及工作，以及他們所提供或可能提供的意見，僅屬有關人士的個人參與及意見，並不代表馬會。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-02-18/208849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2019-02-18%2F208849&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=dbdc6017\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-02-18/208849</a>"},{"pid":"f51b88d2be609ecaaf81b59dd9c5a3769507c720","tid":1026690,"uid":211461,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d294eb535029ecaff32217f882b7dc8aa84f5dd0","tid":1026690,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd55be15120ac29a2fef600a86345c2e13a6eb63","tid":1026690,"uid":81113,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"又呃人"},{"pid":"48142ed098c5d6918cccd6736bedbb05b567b3c2","tid":1026690,"uid":60524,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"隔陣又鳩吹 遲下同美國合作去火星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f26c6f8c50c623f313637d53ed895235ce6aa55","tid":1026690,"uid":191701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"韓幹部果然符合黨情"},{"pid":"50a169aea69f1af12b09258a94a24ca26cda71ba","tid":1026690,"uid":193893,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"今期流行 流行高雄陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我夠係馬會前職員啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d311c17ad4d13a4ba8872f9fbaedf2687fd5e42b","tid":1026690,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:17:20.000Z","msg":"馬會真係衰既啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}